  				<span><span class="alias">Carlsbarls</span></span>
  				<span>on February 15, 2007</span>
  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-1024"><p>What cosmopolitan superiority? See, that&#8217;s where you Pittsburghers go wrong. We don&#8217;t think we&#8217;re better; we just think we&#8217;re here. And some of us think it makes sense to own cars but not a shovel&#8211;those are the ones we could do without. Actually, I&#8217;m going to put <em>I don&#8217;t own a shovel</em> in boldface right now because I can not stop thinking about it.</p></div>
